        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Kenneth Meisel Public Servants' Claimant Fairness Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Labor to revise regulations so as to allow at least 60 days (rather than at least 30 days) for a claimant to submit any additional evidence that is requested by the Office of Workers' Compensation Programs to support a federal workers' compensation claim.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
